data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Parker's Landing! This all-brick beauty boasts 4 bedrooms and a spacious open-concept floor plan offering ample space. Gleaming hardwood floors and luxurious granite countertops adorn the interior, creating a perfect blend of elegance and comfort. The exterior features a large .34 acre lot with privacy to spare. This home is aggressively priced to please call for your private showing today!
